/*
  Vahrheit's Dark Theme for Eyedentity's Dragon Nest forums
  v0.4.0.092820161214
  Fixed sticky topic backgrounds
  Fixed new comment entry box

  v0.3.0.092520161604
  Limit signature sizes

  v0.2.0.092320161904
  Darken tabbars
  Darken Message Center
  Darken user settings
  Fix forum list header being unreadable

  v0.1.1.092320161711
  Fix Latest topics being unreadable
  Fix Search results being unreadable

